1
00:00:32,944 --> 00:00:33,441
[Hei Yan: #1
Bai Xing: #2]

2
00:00:33,466 --> 00:00:34,967
I don't get it.

3
00:00:34,968 --> 00:00:36,335
This is so weird.

4
00:00:36,336 --> 00:00:37,237
Our song is clearly

5
00:00:37,238 --> 00:00:38,437
way better than theirs.

6
00:00:38,438 --> 00:00:40,240
How did Hei Yan take first place again?

7
00:00:41,808 --> 00:00:42,509
This makes no sense.

8
00:00:42,510 --> 00:00:43,610
We still lost.

9
00:00:44,110 --> 00:00:45,411
Wait, weren't you just on stage?

10
00:00:45,412 --> 00:00:46,579
What are you doing here now?

11
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,147
Your artist's set is over,

12
00:00:48,148 --> 00:00:49,228
and you didn't even notice?

13
00:00:49,916 --> 00:00:50,717
We got so many people to call in,

14
00:00:50,717 --> 00:00:51,518
but Bai Bai still lost

15
00:00:51,518 --> 00:00:52,352
to that Hei Yan guy.

16
00:00:52,353 --> 00:00:53,385
Hei Yan's company is massive.

17
00:00:53,386 --> 00:00:54,453
They definitely bought those votes.

18
00:00:54,454 --> 00:00:55,355
Our Bai Bai would never do that.

19
00:00:55,355 --> 00:00:56,189
Next time, we'll bring a bigger crowd.

20
00:00:56,190 --> 00:00:57,190
When we get back, we'll tell Xiaoan

21
00:00:57,191 --> 00:00:58,424
to just buy some ads.

22
00:00:58,425 --> 00:00:59,793
It's not that big of a deal.

23
00:01:00,794 --> 00:01:02,829
Why get so worked up over your pride?

24
00:01:04,364 --> 00:01:05,364
Come on, let's just go.

25
00:01:05,899 --> 00:01:06,766
Fine.

26
00:01:06,767 --> 00:01:08,835
I'll get Xiaoan to handle it later.

27
00:01:09,269 --> 00:01:10,436
What's wrong with buying fan support?

28
00:01:10,437 --> 00:01:11,905
I'm doing all this for you.

29
00:01:12,505 --> 00:01:13,785
Stop giving me such a hard time.

30
00:01:13,973 --> 00:01:16,008
You're just out to get Chen Xiaoan.

31
00:01:16,009 --> 00:01:17,876
You get annoyed every
time he does something.

32
00:01:17,877 --> 00:01:20,212
His company only has one artist,
Bai Xing.

33
00:01:20,213 --> 00:01:21,514
How is he even in your way?

34
00:01:21,748 --> 00:01:23,616
One's 'Black' and the other's 'White'.

35
00:01:24,050 --> 00:01:25,685
I'm honestly sick of both of you.

36
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,220
Hey, Bingchen.

37
00:01:28,221 --> 00:01:29,254
What is it?

38
00:01:29,255 --> 00:01:30,490
Take a look at this.

39
00:01:32,525 --> 00:01:34,427
I'm playing fair, but he's being sneaky.

40
00:01:34,761 --> 00:01:36,596
This 'Black &amp; White' ship thread...

41
00:01:36,963 --> 00:01:39,131
Xiaoan definitely put someone up to this.

42
00:01:39,132 --> 00:01:40,100
Both fanbases

43
00:01:40,101 --> 00:01:41,300
have always hated each other.

44
00:01:41,301 --> 00:01:42,969
Why would they ship you two?

45
00:01:44,204 --> 00:01:45,337
Black and White...

46
00:01:45,338 --> 00:01:46,338
You were really good.

47
00:01:48,808 --> 00:01:49,843
Why'd you stop?

48
00:01:53,179 --> 00:01:54,179
Hey there.

49
00:01:56,749 --> 00:01:58,789
We've been crossing
paths a lot lately, haven't we?

50
00:01:59,185 --> 00:02:01,221
Releasing singles on
the same day and venue...

51
00:02:01,654 --> 00:02:03,590
and now we're sharing a dressing room?

52
00:02:10,730 --> 00:02:12,332
Why are you pushing me?

53
00:02:19,839 --> 00:02:22,007
Your new song is really good.

54
00:02:22,008 --> 00:02:23,343
It really suits you.

55
00:02:24,611 --> 00:02:25,678
Oh, thank you.
